00:22:55,575 --> 00:22:57,710
In the first Chunin
Exam, the person

201
00:22:57,743 --> 00:22:59,712
who served as Exam
proctor was a master

202
00:22:59,712 --> 00:23:01,280
of torture and interrogation.

203
00:23:01,314 --> 00:23:03,416
-Ibiki Morino.

204
00:23:03,449 --> 00:23:04,750
YAMATO: Ah, not finished yet.

205
00:23:04,784 --> 00:23:07,420
The second Exam proctor
for the scroll competition

206
00:23:07,453 --> 00:23:10,289
in the forest of death
had a super sweet tooth.

207
00:23:10,323 --> 00:23:11,891
-Anko Mitarashi.

208
00:23:11,924 --> 00:23:14,460
YAMATO: But the question
is, at the Chunin Exams,

209
00:23:14,460 --> 00:23:16,896
who were the three sound
ninja that received orders

210
00:23:16,929 --> 00:23:17,730
from Orochimaru?

211
00:23:17,763 --> 00:23:19,332
-Oh, yeah, I remember them.

212
00:23:19,365 --> 00:23:20,466
What were their names again?

213
00:23:20,500 --> 00:23:21,767
-I Have no idea.

214
00:23:21,801 --> 00:23:22,735
-Time's up.

215
00:23:22,768 --> 00:23:25,338
We're looking for
Dosu, Zaku, and Kin.

216
00:23:25,371 --> 00:23:26,772
-Sai, you're correct.

217
00:23:26,806 --> 00:23:29,942
And for the record, after
that, Dosu fell prey to Gaara,

218
00:23:29,976 --> 00:23:32,745
while tragically, Zaku
and Kin were sacrificed

219
00:23:32,778 --> 00:23:35,214
for Orochimaru's reanimation.

220
00:23:35,248 --> 00:23:37,316
-So would this be a proper
time for me to smile?

221
00:23:37,350 --> 00:23:39,452
-Don't you dare!

